  "description": "Watchable error-budget burn demo for demo-api. Inject errors/latency with the chaos hooks (CHAOS_ERROR_RATE / /admin/chaos) and drive load with load-test/k6 to watch the 30d error budget drain and the fast/slow burn-rate lines cross their page/ticket thresholds, then recover. Companion to demo-api-overview.json.",
