  "title": "demo-api — Error Budget Burn (Demo)",
  "uid": "demo-api-slo-burn",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": "",
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to watch this demo",
      "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 50,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Error-budget burn demo — what you are watching\nThree phases, left to right on every panel. Add a Grafana **region annotation** (Ctrl/Cmd-drag on any graph) tagged `baseline`, `burn`, or `recovery` to mark them live.\n\n| Phase | What you do | What the panels show |\n|-------|-------------|----------------------|\n| **1 · Baseline** | Steady traffic from `load-test/k6`, chaos OFF | Error rate ~0%, budget **flat at ~100%**, burn rate near **0** |\n| **2 · Burn** | Turn on chaos: `CHAOS_ERROR_RATE` / `CHAOS_LATENCY_MS` (env) or `POST /admin/chaos` | Error rate jumps, **fast (1h) burn** crosses **14.4× (page)**, **slow (6h) burn** lags then crosses **6× / 3×**, **budget remaining drains** |\n| **3 · Recovery** | Chaos OFF (`POST /admin/chaos {error_rate:0}`) | Error rate returns to 0%, burn-rate lines fall back below thresholds, budget remaining stops draining and slowly recovers over the 30d window |\n\nRed/orange vertical lines are auto-annotations for the **fast/slow burn alerts** firing (`ALERTS{...}`). See `observability/README.md` → *Error-budget burn demo*."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Error budget — the headline",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "id": 100,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error Budget Remaining (30d)",
      "description": "Fraction of the 0.1% / 30d error budget still available. 100% = untouched, 0% = exhausted. Drains during the burn phase. Series: slo:error_budget:remaining_ratio30d (burn-demo-rules.yaml).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 1,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 0.25 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0.5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "slo:error_budget:remaining_ratio30d{service=\"demo-api\"}",
          "legendFormat": "budget remaining",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Budget Remaining — gauge",
      "description": "Same series as the stat, as a gauge so the drain during the burn phase is visceral. Green ≥50%, orange ≥25%, red below.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 6 },
      "id": 2,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 0.25 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0.5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "slo:error_budget:remaining_ratio30d{service=\"demo-api\"}",
          "legendFormat": "budget remaining",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Budget Remaining over time (30d window)",
      "description": "Watch this line: flat at ~100% during baseline, draining during burn, flattening/recovering after chaos is turned off. Series: slo:error_budget:remaining_ratio30d.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 2,
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
